    "help": "The current workflow default parameters are rather conservative, aiming for high-quality MAGs.\nTo report lower quality MAGs as well, change the parameters of completeness and contamination.\nThis workflow is maintained by the microGalaxy community. Feel free to reach out for support: [microGalaxy](https://galaxyproject.org/community/sig/microbial)",
